{"tid":407842,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"保連奴算唔算證明左長期吸入霧霾有助身體健康?","createTime":"2017-09-20T17:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T03:55:46.000Z","uid":44748,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cc25f8c6424f4c27b10f9ec401daa2f7aa3e93","tid":407842,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:50:34.000Z","msg":"好簡單 你去到火星/太空 長時間居住 因為地心吸力細左 肌肉或者體質都會變弱<br />\n<br />\n去到中超吸住霧霾踢波就等於幫自己練緊廢活量 同埋係殺人式既搶截下可以練到體格 <br />\n<br />\n所以保連奴依家係中場踢左咁多年就由係英超廢物變成中超球王 再變成1線box to box中場 <br />\n<br />\n但係唔係所有人都有毅力練到 J馬天尼斯去到就斷腳休息左唔知幾耐<br />\n<br />\n不過只要吸住霧霾踢夠357年 就可以成為頂尖球員<br />\n<br />\nTherefore we can prove that 中超球王&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;英超球王(張佰倫 朗尼 阿古路....... etc)<br />\n<br />\n由此證明左長期吸入霧霾有助身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd6a99abf4760dfc047e384ae4dbbf9994616da","tid":407842,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:52:00.000Z","msg":"有沒人同意?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438ff30a9750419bbf2c121e1ad15a6fda0401fb","tid":407842,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:54:44.000Z","msg":"如果成立，你解釋唔到中國點解咁弱"},{"pid":"7e09515a62bfd139ecd703863afc46764f729ebb","tid":407842,"uid":44748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果成立，你解釋唔到中國點解咁弱</blockquote><br />\n整體意識除外 1 on 1實嬴"},{"pid":"d42f4505e2a7af0cc02012735cbf11de3a7668fd","tid":407842,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:15:49.000Z","msg":"見到打咁大篇野,覆下你啦"},{"pid":"36de3e96a297514bfe31d49d66d31d94f50949ce","tid":407842,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果成立，你解釋唔到中國點解咁弱</blockquote><br />\n夜晚通頂踢波，對中國不利牙"},{"pid":"0c3b4e9692d494c01ce163b3b3fe8e00b7c33309","tid":407842,"uid":11185,"like